oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Wagon ride
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of several children riding in a mule-drawn wagon in Linary, Tennessee. They are dressed up to go to the county fair. An unidentified man can also be seen in the wagon, holding the reins.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Carts & wagons; People; Children; Mules
